{"comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOQotRX87pOmom","author":{"login":"coderabbitai"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: summarize by coderabbit.ai -->\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: review paused by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> ## Reviews paused\n> \n> It looks like this branch is under active development. To avoid overwhelming you with review comments due to an influx of new commits, CodeRabbit has automatically paused this review. You can configure this behavior by changing the `reviews.auto_review.auto_pause_after_reviewed_commits` setting.\n> \n> Use the following commands to manage reviews:\n> - `@coderabbitai resume` to resume automatic reviews.\n> - `@coderabbitai review` to trigger a single review.\n> \n> Use the checkboxes below for quick actions:\n> - [ ] <!-- {\"checkboxId\": \"7f6cc2e2-2e4e-497a-8c31-c9e4573e93d1\"} --> ▶️ Resume reviews\n> - [ ] <!-- {\"checkboxId\": \"e9bb8d72-00e8-4f67-9cb2-caf3b22574fe\"} --> 🔍 Trigger review\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: review paused by coderabbit.ai -->\n<!-- walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>📝 Walkthrough</summary>\n\n## Walkthrough\n\nPR lägger till en webhook-server och integration för Antigravity-taskhantering med kvotspårning, uppdaterar MCP-fabrikserverns hälsotjänster och fallback-dispatch, inför nya dokument, tester och verktyg för självhostade runners, samt lägger till en neon-noir inloggningskomponent och CI/E2E-justeringar med PostgreSQL.\n\n## Changes\n\n|Cohort / File(s)|Summary|\n|---|---|\n|**CI/CD & arbetsflöden** <br> `.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml`, `.github/workflows/autonomous-antigravity-trigger.yml`|E2E-workflow: Postgres 15 service, `prisma db push`-steg och env-override för lokal Postgres. Nytt workflow `autonomous-antigravity-trigger.yml` för att signalera Antigravity eller fallback-dispatch via GitHub API.|\n|**Webhook-server (implementering)** <br> `mcp/factory-server/src/webhook-server.ts`, `mcp/factory-server/build/webhook-server.js`|Ny HTTP-server med `POST /webhook/trigger`, HMAC-SHA256-signaturverifiering, health endpoint, CORS, och logik för att skriva `current.md` i agenttasks-katalogen; exporterar start- och signaturfunktioner.|\n|**MCP-fabrikserver (kärna & build)** <br> `mcp/factory-server/src/index.ts`, `mcp/factory-server/build/index.js`|Lägger till getTaskDirectory, hälsoroute, kvotdriven/filbaserad task-signalering, webhook-server start beroende på ENV, och fallback via GitHub workflow dispatch.|\n|**Kvot-/quota-hantering** <br> `mcp/factory-server/src/quota-manager.ts`, `mcp/factory-server/build/quota-manager.js`|Introducerar konfigurerbar `quotaFilePath`, `setQuotaFilePath`, och utökar `QuotaStatus` med `source` ('antigravity' | 'unknown'); `getQuota`/`trackUsage` returnerar nu `source`.|\n|**Dokumentation & guider** <br> `docs/WEBHOOK_INTEGRATION.md`, `docs/ANTIGRAVITY_QUOTA_STRATEGY.md`, `docs/SELF_HOSTED_RUNNER_SETUP.md`|Nya och utökade guider för webhook-integration, Antigravity kvotstrategi och setup för självhostade runners med exempel och felsökning.|\n|**n8n-mallar** <br> `docs/n8n-templates/manual-workflow-trigger.json`, `docs/n8n-templates/scheduled-workflow-trigger.json`, `docs/n8n-templates/README.md`|Två nya n8n-mallar (manuell + schemalagd) som genererar HMAC-signatur och postar mot webhook; README beskriver användning och felsökning.|\n|**Tester** <br> `mcp/factory-server/src/__tests__/*`, `mcp/factory-server/build/__tests__/*`, `mcp/factory-server/vitest.config.ts`|Nya enhetstester för trigger_autonomous_workflow och quota-manager; Vitest-konfigurerad testmiljö och mock/FS-scenarier.|\n|**Webhook-runtime konfig / dev** <br> `.idx/dev.nix`, `.idx/mcp.json`|Lägger till `ENABLE_WEBHOOK_SERVER`, `WEBHOOK_PORT`, samt dev preview-kommando `npm run start:webhook` och port 3030 exposure.|\n|**MCP-paketberoenden** <br> `mcp/factory-server/package.json`, `apps/mcp-n8n/package.json`, `package.json`|`@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` uppgraderad till ^1.25.2; pnpm.overrides för `hono` satt till 4.11.9; test:coverage-script justerat; Vitest config tillagd.|\n|**Frontend: Neon-Noir login** <br> `src/features/auth/NeonNoirLogin.tsx`, `src/features/auth/NeonNoirLogin.stories.tsx`, `src/app/login-neon/page.tsx`|Ny React-komponent med neon-noir UI och Storybook-story; demo-sida exporterad. Ingen backend-autentisering implementerad.|\n|**Analyser & rapporter** <br> `codebase_audit.json`, `security_audit.json`, `outdated_dependencies.json`, `DAILY_BRIEF.md`, `SITE.md`|Nya audit- och säkerhetsfiler samt uppdaterad daglig rapport och site-vision; innehåller CVE-listor, workflow-listor och beroendestatus.|\n|**CI-loggar / debug** <br> `dbguard_log_634.txt`, `verify_log_634.txt`|Inkluderade körloggar visar pnpm lockfile-mismatch och detaljerade CI-händelser för felsökning.|\n|**Övrigt** <br> `scripts/audit-codebase.ps1`, `next-prompt.md`, `prisma/migrations/...`, `src/actions/integrations/intervals.ts`|Audit-script förbättrat för test/docs-kontroll, designskiss för inloggning sida, migration med ny FK, och mindre mapping-justering i intervals.ts.|\n\n## Sekvensdiagram\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant Client\n    participant WebhookServer as Webhook Server\n    participant MCP as MCP Factory<br/>Server\n    participant FileSystem as Task<br/>Directory\n    participant Antigravity\n    participant GitHubActions as GitHub<br/>Actions\n\n    Client->>WebhookServer: POST /webhook/trigger (payload + signature)\n    WebhookServer->>WebhookServer: Verify HMAC-SHA256 signature\n    alt Signature Invalid\n        WebhookServer-->>Client: 401 Error\n    else Valid Signature\n        WebhookServer->>FileSystem: Write current.md (workflow, model, source)\n        FileSystem-->>WebhookServer: Task file created\n        WebhookServer-->>Client: 200 Success (task path)\n        WebhookServer->>MCP: Log task signal\n        MCP->>MCP: trackUsage(1)\n        Antigravity->>FileSystem: Poll current.md\n        Antigravity->>Antigravity: Process task\n        Antigravity->>FileSystem: Remove current.md (completion)\n    end\n```\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant Trigger as Trigger<br/>Request\n    participant MCP as MCP Factory<br/>Server\n    participant TaskDir as Task<br/>Directory\n    participant Antigravity\n    participant GitHubAPI as GitHub<br/>API\n\n    Trigger->>MCP: trigger_autonomous_workflow (workflow, model)\n    MCP->>MCP: getTaskDirectory()\n    alt Antigravity Available\n        MCP->>TaskDir: Write current.md mission signal\n        TaskDir-->>MCP: Signal created\n        MCP->>MCP: trackUsage(1)\n        MCP-->>Trigger: Return 'antigravity'\n        Antigravity->>TaskDir: Poll & process\n        Antigravity->>TaskDir: Remove on complete\n    else Antigravity Unavailable\n        MCP->>GitHubAPI: createWorkflowDispatch (autonomous-antigravity-trigger.yml)\n        GitHubAPI-->>MCP: Workflow queued\n        MCP->>MCP: trackUsage(1)\n        MCP-->>Trigger: Return 'fallback'\n    end\n```\n\n## Uppskattad kodgranskningsinsats\n\n🎯 4 (Komplex) | ⏱️ ~60 minuter\n\n## Dikt\n\n> 🐰 En webhook hoppade in i grinden,  \n> Antigravity-tasken svävar på vinden,  \n> Neon-noir lyser vid inloggningsdörren,  \n> Kvoter räknas tyst och filer tar spår,  \n> Fallback dansar redo när molnet tar störten.\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- tips_start -->\n\n---\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> <details>\n> <summary>🎁 Summarized by CodeRabbit Free</summary>\n> \n> Your organization is on the Free plan. CodeRabbit will generate a high-level summary and a walkthrough for each pull request. For a comprehensive line-by-line review, please upgrade your subscription to CodeRabbit Pro by visiting <https://app.coderabbit.ai/login>.\n> \n> </details>\n\n<sub>Comment `@coderabbitai help` to get the list of available commands and usage tips.</sub>\n\n<!-- tips_end -->\n\n<!-- internal state start -->\n\n\n<!--  -->\n\n<!-- internal state end -->","createdAt":"2026-02-17T07:59:39Z","includesCreatedEdit":tru